name: Photographer (exsanguination)
description:
"Good Morning My Love, Did You Sleep Well?" series no.1
This belongs to a series of three pieces.

•Photographer•
Later, in purgatory, I found out that he also cut my throat😑. I feel it was very unnecessary since he suffocated me before it wasn't like I could run, scream, or anything else. Anyway, I wasn't happy or sad that I'm dead but at least I wore my best bra that day! Honestly! it was my favorite and it matched with his new light in the bathroom. I miss talking to him while going through his old photographs I always thought those were models, not A REAL DEAD GIRL.
